      "instruction": "<p>Preheat the oven to 220°C/ 200°C (fan)/ gas 7</p><p>Add your <strong>meaty pulled mushrooms </strong>to an <strong>oven-proof dish </strong>with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and put the dish in the oven for an initial 20 min</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1670922465689-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1670922465689-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1670922465689-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1670922465689-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1670922465689-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Cut your <strong>potatoes</strong> (skins on) into fries</p><p>Add the <strong>fries</strong> to a baking tray with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and put the tray in the oven for 20-25 min or until golden and crisp</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1670922472467-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1670922472467-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1670922472467-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1670922472467-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1670922472467-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, add your <strong>mooli slaw mix</strong> and <strong>rice vinegar</strong> to a large bowl with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/1 tsp] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up and set aside – this is your <strong>quick-pickled mooli slaw</strong></p>",
      "order": 3,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1670922480034-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1670922480034-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1670922480034-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1670922480034-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-3-1670922480034-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Peel and grate your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>grated garlic</strong>, <strong>five-spice mix</strong>, <strong>hoisin sauce</strong>, <strong>agave </strong>and <strong>soy sauce </strong>in a bowl</p><p>Add 125ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[175ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[200ml]</span> <strong>cold water </strong>and a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and stir everything together – this is your <strong>char siu-style sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 4,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1670922486459-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1670922486459-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1670922486459-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1670922486459-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-4-1670922486459-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine your <strong>sriracha </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and<strong> mayo</strong> in a small bowl – this is your <strong>sriracha mayo</strong></p><p>Pick your <strong>coriander leaves</strong> from the stalks, discard the stalks</p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1670922491670-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1670922491670-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1670922491670-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1670922491670-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1670922491670-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>After an initial 20 min, remove the dish with the meaty pulled mushrooms from the oven</p><p>Spoon the <strong>char siu-style sauce </strong>over the mushrooms and return them to the oven for 10-12 min further, basting them twice more until the sauce is thick and the mushrooms are nicely glazed – these are your<strong> char siu-style pulled mushrooms</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1670922501793-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1670922501793-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1670922501793-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1670922501793-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1670922501793-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Pierce your <strong>bao bun packet[s]</strong> with a few holes and <strong>microwave</strong> for 1-2 min</p><p>To build your buns, fill each <strong>bao bun</strong> with the <strong>char siu-styled pulled mushrooms</strong> and top with some of the <strong>quick-pickled mooli slaw</strong></p><p>Drizzle over a little of the <strong>sriracha mayo</strong> and garnish with<strong> half</strong> of the <strong>crispy onions </strong>and <strong>coriander leaves </strong>(save the rest for later!)<strong> </strong>– these are your <strong>char siu-style mushroom bao buns</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1670922513866-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1670922513866-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1670922513866-x700.jpg",
            "width": 700
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1670922513866-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1670922513866-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>char siu-style mushroom bao buns </strong>with the <strong>fries </strong>and <strong>remaining quick-pickled mooli slaw </strong>to the side</p><p>Load up the fries with<strong> </strong>any<strong> remaining sriracha mayo</strong>, <strong>crispy</strong> <strong>onions</strong> and <strong>coriander leaves</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
      "order": 8,
